lines: REDEEMED! HOW I LOVE TO PROCLAIM IT
Ndafutuka aluse lwakwe Ndibe mwana wakwe lyonse.
Jesu ula ndikomanisya Ku komanisya kupati
Ndizyi kuti ku mweka kwakwe Kuya kukala andime.
Ndayeeya Mufutuli wangu Zuba lyoonse nda muyeeya
Ndilaimba nse kaumuni Kuimba luyando lwakwe.
Ndazyiba ndiya ku mubona Mwami oyo undiyanda
Ula ndisololela koonse A kundibamba masiku.
